<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4359050>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 18. Micrographs of Marionina clavata Nielsen & Christensen, 1961. A. Clitellar glands, dorsal view. B. Clitellar glands absent midventrally, latero-ventral view (penial bulbs marked with arrows). C–E. Club-shaped, hollow oesophageal appendages (ph=pharyngeal glands). F. Nephridia. G. Sperm funnel. H–I. Spermathecae. All in vivo. Scale bars 50 μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4359050/files/figure.png" .

